WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.720
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.720 --> 00:00:07.800
Well, I have a hard word to give, but first off, I want to tell you all thank you for praying for me.

00:00:07.800 --> 00:00:11.874
Thank you for being here and being a part of this family, this prayer channel.

00:00:11.874 --> 00:00:19.140
You know, I was going to do this word yesterday and I was going to tell you what the Lord is showing me concerning America and what's coming.

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:21.600
But I didn't want to come out and just give it.

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:22.631
I wanted to pray over it.

00:00:22.862 --> 00:00:26.098
Yesterday, like I said, I was driving around and the Lord gave me the word.

00:00:26.098 --> 00:00:29.546
He said, 'I want you to go home and I want you to dig in the flower beds.

00:00:29.546 --> 00:00:32.228
I want you to go outside and pull weeds right now.

00:00:32.228 --> 00:00:34.632
' I said, 'Well, I'm going to go in and do the video.

00:00:34.632 --> 00:00:35.394
' He said, 'No, you're not.

00:00:35.394 --> 00:00:38.399
You're going to go outside and pull weeds.

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:39.751
' I said, 'Yes, sir.

00:00:39.751 --> 00:00:51.102
' So, I was out there just praying in the spirit and just pulling weeds in the flower bed all afternoon and just praying and asking Him, 'So, what do you want me to say?

00:00:51.102 --> 00:00:52.320
' And He said, 'Nothing yet.

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.200
Go low.

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:54.080
Go slow.

00:00:54.080 --> 00:00:55.269
Go low inside.

00:00:55.269 --> 00:00:55.577
Go deep inside.

00:00:56.194 --> 00:00:59.360
Pray in the spirit and go slow about it.

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:00.937
Don't be quick to deliver a word.

00:01:00.937 --> 00:01:01.726
There's no urgency.

00:01:01.726 --> 00:01:03.440
' And He gave me the scriptures.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:13.829
He said, 'Ephesians 5:1: Be an imitator of God, as dear children imitate their earthly fathers.

00:01:14.674 --> 00:01:15.720
Imitate the Lord.

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:17.874
' And I was like, 'So what do you mean by that?

00:01:17.874 --> 00:01:25.120
' And He started talking about how He wasn't quick to go out and raise Lazarus from the dead.

00:01:25.120 --> 00:01:29.006
The urgency was there and everybody was pushing Him, saying, 'Lazarus is sick.

00:01:29.006 --> 00:01:34.240
He's dying,' and all the things were going around—all the voices around Him.

00:01:35.520 --> 00:01:48.320
He was hearing Lazarus is sick and dying, and all the voices around Him were trying to pressure Him to move out of what God was telling Him to do, which was stay still, peace, peace.

00:01:48.700 --> 00:01:54.440
Four days go by, and Jesus goes, and they said, 'He stinks, Lord.

00:01:54.440 --> 00:02:00.000
' So there was no urgency in His spirit except to follow what the Father had told Him to do.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:03.320
Then He started bringing up Mary and Martha.

00:02:04.300 --> 00:02:10.627
Mary was sitting at the feet of Jesus, listening to Him, staying vertical.

00:02:10.627 --> 00:02:12.766
She didn't do what Martha was doing.

00:02:12.766 --> 00:02:25.486
Martha was in there probably throwing pots and pans around, getting all upset because nobody was in there helping her, because she felt it was urgent to cook the food for all the disciples and for Jesus.

00:02:25.486 --> 00:02:31.560
And so Mary is doing what we should be doing, staying at the feet of Jesus.

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:37.599
There's no urgency when you're in peace like that, is what the Lord was showing me.

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:39.400
Be an imitator of God.

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:40.800
What did Jesus do?

00:02:40.800 --> 00:02:45.184
He stayed, and He heard the Father's voice concerning Lazarus.

00:02:45.184 --> 00:02:47.627
And what did Mary do?

00:02:47.627 --> 00:02:48.760
She stayed at His feet.

00:02:48.760 --> 00:02:53.510
Martha was out there doing all the busy work, but she should have been at the feet, too.

00:02:53.510 --> 00:03:03.040
The urgency of the hour is staying at the feet of Jesus, not being moved by the circumstances of what you're seeing in the news, thinking, 'I've got to come out and tell everybody what the Lord is saying.

00:03:03.040 --> 00:03:07.120
' And the Lord said, 'No, pull weeds.

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:08.766
' I said, 'Whoa, I don't understand.

00:03:08.766 --> 00:03:11.160
' But it's called dying to self, and it's His channel.

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:18.240
And that's what He was trying to get across to me: no matter how much you think you need to deliver a word because you know it's important, this is more important.

00:03:18.240 --> 00:03:23.760
'I need you to rest.

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:27.626
I need you to stay right here at my feet right now, vertical.

00:03:27.626 --> 00:03:30.311
There's much that I need to talk to you about.

00:03:30.311 --> 00:03:38.040
And the only way you're going to hear what I'm going to tell you is by staying right here like Mary.

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:42.903
Don't be Martha right now, Brandon.

00:03:42.903 --> 00:03:43.970
Stay at my feet.

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:49.919
' There are a lot of people being Marthas, and they're running around trying to make the first video and be the first.

00:03:49.919 --> 00:03:56.040
He said, 'But it's more important to be accurate, and the only way you stay accurate is staying at my feet.

00:03:56.040 --> 00:03:57.360
Pull weeds.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:04:05.560
' And I was like, you know, you have all these things going, 'Well, I've got to pull weeds.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:07.120
Be still.

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:12.595
' Do you know how hard it is sometimes when you feel like you haven't heard the word and you're going, 'Well, Lord, you gave me the word, so...

00:04:12.595 --> 00:04:17.950
' But here I was, and I started praying in the spirit, and you know what He started doing?

00:04:17.950 --> 00:04:21.519
He started showing me flowers.

00:04:21.939 --> 00:04:27.504
I started praying in the spirit and I'm looking and seeing if He's going to show me anything else, and He started showing me flowers.

00:04:27.504 --> 00:04:31.707
I saw beautiful lavender flowers that looked like heaven.

00:04:31.707 --> 00:04:37.226
It was glimpses, and I started weeping because of the beauty of the flowers.

00:04:37.226 --> 00:04:40.023
And He said, 'Remember, just like George Washington Carver, Brandon.

00:04:40.023 --> 00:04:55.120
He was the man that talked with the flowers, and God showed him the secret things because he put God first, and he didn't let the clutter cloud his mind of what was going on around him.

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:59.690
He took time to spend with the Great Creator every single day at four o'clock in the morning.

00:04:59.690 --> 00:05:07.213
And no matter how much was going around him, he would always talk to the peanut, and the peanut shared its secrets with him.

00:05:07.213 --> 00:05:09.583
' George Washington Carver was a great man of God.

00:05:09.583 --> 00:05:21.657
And so I want to tell you, for what I'm about to tell you, this came later—more of what He was showing me is in store: 'A great shaking to awaken.

00:05:21.657 --> 00:05:24.060
' He keeps talking to me about it.

00:05:24.060 --> 00:05:26.815
And at this time, I was so tired.

00:05:26.815 --> 00:05:36.040
I was dozing off, and all of a sudden He wanted to talk more about what's coming, and I had heavy eyes.

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:40.248
I was on the couch, and I was bobbing, doing the old bob.

00:05:40.895 --> 00:05:43.300
All of a sudden, He said, 'I have something to say.

00:05:43.300 --> 00:05:44.560
' And I went, 'Yes, sir.

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:45.340
What's going on?

00:05:45.340 --> 00:05:49.140
' You know, and I started praying, and I'm talking down low.

00:05:50.039 --> 00:05:52.329
I said, 'Well, Lord, you picked a real fine time.

00:05:52.329 --> 00:05:53.893
' But it's not in my time; it's in Yours.

00:05:54.107 --> 00:05:56.869
It was when my flesh was out of the way.

00:05:56.869 --> 00:06:00.720
I was completely exhausted, and I told my son, 'Grab the recorder.

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:06.328
' I said, 'The Father's going to talk, and I'm really tired right now, but I'm going to say what He says.

00:06:06.328 --> 00:06:13.240
' But I was dead to my flesh at that point instead of being like a chicken with its head cut off, flapping its wings all around.

00:06:13.980 --> 00:06:18.639
It was at the time when my flesh was out of the way and He could talk the loudest.

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:22.830
And I said, 'You know, Lord, You really are so amazing to me.

00:06:22.830 --> 00:06:26.880
' 'Focus on the flowers today, Brandon.

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:27.680
Focus on the flowers.

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:31.520
' And there will be a lot of you who say, 'Oh, Brandon, get to it.

00:06:31.520 --> 00:06:33.440
' I just did.

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:33.707
I just did.

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:41.553
I just told you a vital piece of the puzzle that many of you will try to bypass because you're so busy.

00:06:41.553 --> 00:06:46.960
But like the Lord is always telling me, He said, 'You're in a hurry to go nowhere.

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:47.967
Nothing else matters.

00:06:47.967 --> 00:06:51.940
Everything that you're trying to achieve on this earth is going to be gone.

00:06:51.940 --> 00:07:00.400
' Most people are trying to build their future and all these great things, the wealth and all the things on this earth.

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:04.983
But the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, sow the seeds for the thousand years.

00:07:04.983 --> 00:07:07.991
Sow the seeds for what you'll reap on the other side.

00:07:07.991 --> 00:07:10.679
For what you sow in secret, you'll be rewarded openly.

00:07:10.679 --> 00:07:12.119
' So, this is what I saw.

00:07:12.119 --> 00:07:15.423
You know, a lot of people are focused on the peace agreement.

00:07:15.423 --> 00:07:20.171
They're saying, 'Hey, we're going to have a ceasefire and all these things.

00:07:20.171 --> 00:07:28.880
' And if you go back to the video where I was praying—I gave a short on it back in December—the Lord showed me that they'll call peace and safety.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:30.160
There'll be peace agreements.

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:37.640
So, we go to what the Lord's already showed us, and now we're seeing it in the news seven months later.

00:07:37.640 --> 00:07:46.479
Seven months later, and He's warning about sudden destruction, major attacks still coming.

00:07:46.479 --> 00:07:50.920
They are not satisfied with what they have achieved.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:55.600
Iran is saying this because they lost so much.

00:07:55.600 --> 00:08:03.299
They dumped billions and billions of dollars into their nuclear program and it was completely wiped out.

00:08:03.299 --> 00:08:08.631
A lot of it—I don't think all of it, in my opinion, of what I've seen in the spirit.

00:08:08.631 --> 00:08:12.052
Not all of it, but a big majority of it.

00:08:12.052 --> 00:08:19.760
And the Lord showed me still to come a major revival in Iran—a major, major revival.

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:28.960
As they're distracted, the infrastructure of things is going to be very crippled, set back by decades.

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:34.586
The Lord said, 'like the Stone Age, back in the decades,' because they're going to be delayed big time.

00:08:34.586 --> 00:08:40.080
But I saw infrastructure problems with the electricity, with a lot of things.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:43.510
And the Lord even talked about oil.

00:08:43.510 --> 00:08:47.240
So with all that being said, what was the next thing I told you?

00:08:47.240 --> 00:08:52.680
I warned you about a biological attack coming out of Syria.

00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:59.623
And many people, when they saw the World War II video, they said, 'Brandon, you said there would be a great betrayal.

00:08:59.623 --> 00:09:02.969
' And I said, 'Wait, it's still coming.

00:09:04.571 --> 00:09:06.536
Wait, it's still coming.

00:09:06.536 --> 00:09:14.983
' I see these are different visions for different scenarios, and it's not all about what's happening right now.

00:09:14.983 --> 00:09:19.200
This is like an onion; it has a lot of layers.

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:27.429
And the next thing I believe we're going to see is a major attack against Syria as Iran retaliates.

00:09:27.429 --> 00:09:43.559
And the Houthis, the rebels, and these people out of Syria will use some kind of biological weapon, and they will attack them, and Damascus will become a ruinous heap when this takes place.

00:09:43.559 --> 00:09:47.627
I saw Turkey come to the aid of a wounded brother.

00:09:47.627 --> 00:09:49.017
I even have the video.

00:09:49.017 --> 00:10:01.920
This is exactly what the Lord said: they will come to the aid of a wounded brother, and all the other Arab nations will be furious when Israel strikes Syria in the days ahead.

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:06.160
They weren't upset so much about Iran.

00:10:06.540 --> 00:10:12.959
The Lord said this was a red-headed stepchild to their faith.

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:16.982
But Syria is pure blood to them; they're upset about this for some reason.

00:10:16.982 --> 00:10:22.811
And I don't understand all this stuff—the Shiites and the Sunnis and all that stuff.

00:10:22.811 --> 00:10:25.920
It's because, you know, it's just not what I know.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:29.769
But the Lord said, 'When they attack Syria, son, you're going to see a great uprising.

00:10:29.769 --> 00:10:33.239
' But not only that, there will be troops on the ground.

00:10:33.239 --> 00:10:39.160
A major, major war will break out when this takes place, but this is later.

00:10:39.160 --> 00:10:41.120
But I've warned you.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:42.320
When does this happen?

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:43.219
I don't know.

00:10:43.219 --> 00:10:58.818
But I've warned you about an uprising of financial things with crypto and oil, and things with the uprising of the Antichrist and all this stuff in the days ahead where you see the changing of the tide.

00:10:58.818 --> 00:10:59.600
It's coming.

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:05.100
It's coming, going from Western to Middle Eastern, and you're going to see an uprising of things.

00:11:05.100 --> 00:11:07.456
And I've told you, a new industrial revolution.

00:11:07.456 --> 00:11:19.200
I've warned you about a lot of stuff, and to go and rehearse every vision right now would be redundant and take too much time, and there are a lot of you who don't want to take that time.

00:11:19.200 --> 00:11:37.954
But I rehearsed you about the Macy's and all the things that I've told you to pray over—the Fourth of July, praying over our nation, our churches, our mega-churches, from Joel Osteen to Steven Furtick, the mega-churches in this nation.

00:11:38.800 --> 00:11:43.093
And then I saw that judgment begin in the house of the Lord.

00:11:43.093 --> 00:11:52.102
It was a two-sided thing: you would see fear about people gathering together, and then there's correction coming to churches.

00:11:52.102 --> 00:12:01.910
I saw in California and other mega-churches that there will be a major cleansing of the house because there's been hidden sin.

00:12:02.970 --> 00:12:04.640
That's been another part of this.

00:12:04.640 --> 00:12:07.500
Okay, so what do I see right now?

00:12:07.500 --> 00:12:12.217
What I saw yesterday: I saw major cyberattacks coming.

00:12:12.217 --> 00:12:15.160
I saw major cyberattacks coming.

00:12:15.160 --> 00:12:27.880
And when it happens, I saw the electric grid in major cities being cyberattacked, and I saw the people that were behind this.

00:12:27.880 --> 00:12:29.770
I saw the dragon.

00:12:29.770 --> 00:12:31.300
I saw Iran.

00:12:31.300 --> 00:12:37.200
There was more to this unfolding than just Iran in the days ahead.

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:50.000
Okay, so do you know about our planes and all the weirdness that's been going on with our flights, and people landing wrong, doing things right?

00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:58.399
Planes flipping upside down—weird stuff that we've never seen before, a lot of uneasiness about flying.

00:12:58.399 --> 00:13:02.160
I saw cyberattacks on planes.

00:13:02.160 --> 00:13:13.600
I saw certain airlines that start with an A being attacked because of their name.

00:13:13.600 --> 00:13:26.240
Then I saw people flying in these jets and their screens going black, like a fuse messed up or something.

00:13:28.470 --> 00:13:36.840
I don't know how it happens, it just goes, and I saw all their instruments, and all of a sudden, the plane falls out of the sky.

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:39.999
Great confusion when it comes to this.

00:13:48.380 --> 00:13:48.750
I saw the radars and the flight decks of all the major airports going dark.

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:57.910
Confusion, not knowing how to tell the pilots where to be in the skies, like a movie.

00:13:58.693 --> 00:14:16.399
This was very real and very detailed in this vision, seeing this great confusion coming to certain airline industries, trying to get people to be afraid to fly.

00:14:16.399 --> 00:14:22.480
Then I saw a major bank, and on the bank, one of the words starts with an A.

00:14:22.480 --> 00:14:26.057
That's similar to the airplane—they're kind of the same.

00:14:26.057 --> 00:14:27.760
That's what I'm going to tell you.

00:14:27.760 --> 00:14:34.651
And when this takes place, I saw people not being able to get their money out because the computers were down.

00:14:34.651 --> 00:14:43.413
ATMs—I saw people at the ATM trying to put their card in, and all the ATMs at that certain bank were completely black.

00:14:43.413 --> 00:15:03.199
They weren't able to have banking because there was a cyberattack with the banks, and people were panicking, trying to get their money out, and they couldn't because the banks were down, trying to mess with the economy.

00:15:03.199 --> 00:15:11.904
Okay, when I saw the grid for the electricity and the cyberattacks, it was in New York.

00:15:11.904 --> 00:15:15.839
I saw New York City—I saw the Big Apple, right?

00:15:15.839 --> 00:15:19.839
What you would say, but it was like a major American city.

00:15:21.245 --> 00:15:27.360
I saw darkness on all of the major buildings.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:40.480
And they were shining lights somehow—I don't know how, like generators trying to shine lights to create power because they didn't want people to loot.

00:15:40.800 --> 00:15:46.340
Spotlights, you know, trying to make things look brighter in the city by generators.

00:15:46.340 --> 00:15:53.246
And I saw light shining on the buildings for reflection, because it's kind of mirrored on the glass of the buildings.

00:15:53.246 --> 00:15:59.759
But they were trying to make it where it was trying to glow because it was so dark in the city.

00:15:59.759 --> 00:16:01.360
And that's really interesting.

00:16:01.360 --> 00:16:08.870
I don't know, it's just what I saw, and I'm just telling you what I saw—trying to shine it off the building.

00:16:08.880 --> 00:16:11.280
So I saw all that.

00:16:11.280 --> 00:16:13.680
I saw the FAA—cyberattacks coming to the FAA.

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:23.040
And I saw darkness on Cuba—darkness like a complete grid-down.

00:16:27.693 --> 00:16:30.352
And this was on purpose and in retaliation.

00:16:31.215 --> 00:16:40.870
There are things there that are not being said because they're making ties with Russia.

00:16:40.880 --> 00:16:49.645
And because of these ties with Russia, certain entities are trying to influence—they see it, they know it's coming, they know what they're doing.

00:16:49.645 --> 00:16:53.839
And there's darkness coming to Cuba.

00:16:53.839 --> 00:17:03.239
I saw darkness on it, and I don't know why—some kind of cyber, I don't know, but I saw darkness.

00:17:03.239 --> 00:17:04.502
And I've told you that.

00:17:04.502 --> 00:17:12.586
And the mules left during the darkness—the mules left trying to be in the cover of night.

00:17:12.586 --> 00:17:15.199
There's more to this.

00:17:15.199 --> 00:17:26.480
But what we saw at the beginning of the year with planes doing certain things that seemed kind of off was cyber.

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:29.360
There's more cyber to this.

00:17:29.360 --> 00:17:34.622
So I tell you all this not to create fear, but to warn you.

00:17:34.622 --> 00:17:42.811
You know, when I saw all the fish floating in the water because of the volcanoes that are about to erupt, and I saw the major attacks.

00:17:42.811 --> 00:17:51.554
And the Lord kept bringing up Timothy McVeigh to me, and I thought, 'Lord, why do you keep talking about Timothy McVeigh?

00:17:51.554 --> 00:17:54.617
' Y'all let the elevator go to the top, Brandon.

00:17:54.617 --> 00:17:59.360
It's because the Lord said, 'Brandon, it's what he used.

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:00.960
It's what he used.

00:18:00.960 --> 00:18:06.150
I'm telling you, don't forget Timothy McVeigh because I'm trying to talk to you.

00:18:06.150 --> 00:18:09.280
' It's like code he's trying to tell me—it's what he used.

00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:15.600
And folks, I've already warned you in January about the fertilizer.

00:18:15.600 --> 00:18:25.968
And I thought, 'Well, that's interesting,' because I added it together, because when I'm hearing something, I just repeat what I hear, and I just go, 'This is what I hear: don't forget Timothy McVeigh.

00:18:25.968 --> 00:18:31.808
' And I'm like, 'Okay, well, that doesn't make any sense to me in the natural, but I'll say it.

00:18:31.808 --> 00:18:35.919
' And I say it, and then I'm asking Him, and I just go into prayer by myself and I...

00:18:35.919 --> 00:18:36.764
Can I ask a question?

00:18:36.764 --> 00:18:38.100
Why do you keep saying that?

00:18:38.760 --> 00:18:41.173
It doesn't make any sense to me.

00:18:41.538 --> 00:18:42.631
That man's dead.

00:18:42.631 --> 00:18:43.931
He was executed.

00:18:43.931 --> 00:18:47.407
He says, "It's because of how he did it and what he did.

00:18:47.407 --> 00:18:52.240
" And I said, "Oh my gosh, I was just a kid.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:53.040
" I remember.

00:18:53.040 --> 00:18:57.679
So my son, we all googled; he used the fertilizer.

00:18:57.679 --> 00:19:01.360
And the Lord told me, "I want you to remember the bomb.

00:19:02.560 --> 00:19:04.100
This stuff is still...

00:19:04.100 --> 00:19:06.000
you need to pray this.

00:19:06.000 --> 00:19:09.480
This is very serious stuff that I'm talking about right now, folks.

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:22.280
